devdoc.author: @psychoplasma
devdoc.details: Interface to access to Register contract from corresponding proxy contract.

exchangeTokensForEth(address,uint256).details: ???Can be called only through Proxy contract

hasKitties(address).details: Checks whether there is a kittie registered to the system under the given account.
hasKitties(address).return: bool true if there is a kittie registered to the system under the given account

initialize().details: Sets related database contracts and tokens ProfileDB, RoleDB, CryptoKitties, KittieFightToken, SuperDAOTokenCan be called only by the owner of this contract

isRegistered(address).details: Checks whether there is a profile on ProfileDB with the given address.
isRegistered(address).return: bool true if there is a registered profile with the given address, false otherwise.

lockKittie(address,uint256).details: Locks the given CryptoKitty to this contract. Prior to this operation, the owner of the given CryptoKitty should approve this contract for trasfer operation.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the owner of CryptoKitty to be locked
params.kittieId: uint256 Id of CryptoKitty to be locked

lockTokens(address,uint256).details: Locks KittieFight tokens to this contract and saves the locked amount on ProfileDB under account's profile.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the user whose tokens will be locked
params.amount: uint256 Amount of KittieFight tokens to be locked

payFees(address,uint256).details: ???Can be called only through Proxy contract

register(address).details: Creates a new profile with the given address in ProfileDB and sets its role to `bettor` by default.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the user to be registered

releaseKittie(address,uint256).details: Transfers the given CryptoKitty from this contract to its user. The kitten's status should not be dead/ghots nor playing. Otherwise the tx will be reverted.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the owner of CryptoKitty to be released
params.kittieId: uint256 Id of CryptoKitty to be released

releaseTokens(address,uint256).details: Releases KittieFight tokens from this contract to `account`. Does not allow to release an amount more than the locked amount. Updates the locked amount on ProfileDB accordingly after release.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the user whose tokens will be released
params.amount: uint256 Amount of KittieFight tokens to be released

sendTokensTo(address,address,uint256).details: ???Can be called only through Proxy contract

stakeSuperDAO(address,uint256).details: Stakes SuperDAO tokens to this contract and saves the stake amount and staking status on ProfileDB.Can be called only through Proxy contract

params.account: address Address of the user who is staking
params.amount: uint256 Amount of SuperDAO tokens to be staked

updateKittie(string,address,uint256,uint.details: Updates the status of the given kitten.Can be called through other system contracts

params.account: address Address of the owner of CryptoKitty to be updated
params.contractName: string Address of the owner of CryptoKitty to be updated
params.deadAt: uint256 Time of death of the kitten if its status dead
params.kittieId: uint256 Id of CryptoKitty to be updated
params.kittieStatus: string Status of the kitten in KittieFight system
